Package: TRNValStandVis
Title: Validate, Standardize and Visualize TF-TG networks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mogtaba", "Alim", , "mogtaba.alim@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: `TRNValStandVis` is an R package that consolidates transcription factor-target gene (TF-TG) interaction data from MSigDB, hTFtarget, ChEA3, and TFLink into a single HGNC-compliant dataset. It evaluates the quality of TF-TG interactions and provides a score for each TF's overall quality. The package also visualizes TF-TG regulons and networks, compares TFs qualitatively, and standardizes nomenclature and validation metrics for TF-TG interactions. 
